{"tid":1874991,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】世衞總幹事︰病毒構成「非常嚴重威脅」 籲全球團結對抗疫情","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:58:23.000Z","uid":28114,"like":10,"dislike":183,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"5897a9f7c002c3bd3c84a85fc892afa0de575381","tid":1874991,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200211/large/1581415740_6268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581415740_6268.jpg&h=68bc1d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚德塞（右二）形容肺炎病毒對全球構成嚴重威脅。<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n世界衞生組織（WHO）周二起一連兩天舉行研討加快開發武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎（WARS）治療藥物、診斷劑和疫苗會議，總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）在會上表示，新型冠狀病毒「對全球其他地方構成嚴重威脅」，呼籲大家分享病毒樣本，加快研究治療藥物及疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞在會上向逾400名專家表示，目前單單中國境內已錄得逾4.2萬宗確診個案，死亡人數亦逾1,000人，「中國確診病例佔全球99%，對中國而言情況緊急，但仍對全球其他地區構成嚴重威脅」。<br />\n新型冠狀病毒全球肆虐，但關於病毒的起源仍未能確定，譚德塞稱「我們希望今次會議其中一個成果，就是落實研究路線圖，讓研究人員及捐助者可以跟隨，在共享樣本和成果方面，最重要是團結、團結、團結。我們要戰勝這場疫情，便要根據公平原則一起分享。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200211/J53VQGSVMO7SRS2CNEYED46VEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200211%2FJ53VQGSVMO7SRS2CNEYED46VEI%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7b265d33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200211%2FJ53VQGSVMO7SRS2CNEYED46VEI%2F&h=d772ab5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200211/J53VQGSVMO7SRS2CNEYED46VEI/</a>"},{"pid":"d14dd3bdda9b1de8481258a4a63aa84341551f9e","tid":1874991,"uid":28114,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"共產黨俾唔到尾數佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aaa61b9e0a495b3ea76c2b2673fac53e57a5a4","tid":1874991,"uid":32722,"like